<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="response-n">response <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'spɒns/    美 /rɪ'spɑːns/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>回答；反应：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a quick response 
迅速的答复</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>make</strong> no <strong>response</strong> to the question 
没有对提问作答</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>bring / produce response 
引起/产生反响</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-response-to">in response (to)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>作为 (对…的) 回答 / 反应：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The government acted in response to economic pressure. 
政府为应对经济压力采取了行动。</p></div></div>